Hello MIGHTY LIONS,
We have missed you all!!!
We are please to announce that We will have a drive thru Graduation ceremony for Kindergarten and 8th grade on Friday May 22nd.
We are asking that you stay in yours cars as we hand out the diplomas. We must still follow the Covid-19 rules. Each car will drive through and the teachers will hand out the diploma to the graduate.
Kindergarten will be from 10-11:30 am
8th Grade will be from 12pm- 1:30 pm
We look forward to seeing our graduates on Friday!!!!!

post_text: Good afternoon Riverside families. Today we performed a lock down drill at the request of the Cincinnati Police Department. They will put a school on lock down when there is something that is unsafe happening in the general area of the school. Today something was going on in the apartments on Hillside right by the school. All of our students performed perfectly and did an amazing job. We are extremely proud of our Lions. Again there was no danger at the school and everything resumed to normal very quickly. LETS GO LIONS!!!!!!!!!!!!

post_text:
Re-Enrollment for 2017-2018
Current students may re-enroll for the coming school year from February 1, 2017 until February 28, 2017.
Re-enrollment forms have been mailed home and should be received before February 1.
We must receive your student's Re-enrollment Indication Form by February 28, 2017 to reserve a seat for your student.
Staring March 1, 2017, we will begin enrolling students new to the school.
